https://api.github.com/search/repositories?q=language:csharp+created:2016-01-01..2016-01-05+size:%3E10000&per_page=100


List languages for the specified repository. The value on the right of a language is the number of bytes of code written in that language.

GET /repos/:owner/:repo/languages
eg. https://api.github.com/repos/lixiangers/BadgeUtil/languages
Response
Status: 200 OK
{
  "C": 78769,
  "Python": 7769
}

